import classes from './TestSite.module.css'; const TestStartInfoPage=(props)=>{ return

Celpip Practice Test Id: 2

Do not refresh the browser while taking the test!

  1. You should give yourself 2 hours and 39 minutes to complete CELPIP-General Practice Test A. Press Start to contunue to the test. Test cannot be paused once started. You cannot go back once test starts. Be prepared before starting the test.
  2. Once you have completed the test, you can consult the examiner for Performance Standards of Writing and Speaking to understand how your responses would be evaluated by CELPIP Raters. Please be sure to save your Writing responses and record your Speaking responses so you can review them later using the Performance Standards.
  3. You will need a headset or speakers for the Listening and Speaking components of the test. The practice test will record your Speaking responses. We advise you to set up your recording device of laptop prior to starting the speaking section. For optimal performance, your computer should have a minimum resolution of 1368 x 768. Paper and pencils will be provided at the offical test for note-taking, so before you begin this sample test make sure that you have paper and a pen or pencil, since you may want to take notes.
} export default TestStartInfoPage;
